metadata.name: Lau Hu Pao #0001
metadata.description: Celebrating the year of Tiger, Lau Hu Pao is a 3,333 generative hand drawn Tiger art collection by former Disney chief and artist MochSarm. Each Tiger art features cool and aesthetically appealing outfit and accessories with the artist's trademark stroke style applied on all of the art. May this year of Tiger gives Lau Hu Pao holder the courage and confidence to put brilliant ideas into practice while remains generous and always stands up for the weak.
